data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT!!   MAKE THIS ONE YOUR NEXT FLORIDA HOME!  Located behind the gates of the premier resort community of River Strand Golf and Country Club, this GOLF DEEDED property is waiting for its next owner!  At over 2600 sq ft, the Bayhill model offers both separation and so much space!   The family room /kitchen combination is ideal, with the large heart of the home gathering area overlooked by the well equipped eat-in kitchen with breakfast bar, the space is both open and bright.   A dining area perfect for larger gatherings  and an additional living / seating  area also provide additional space to relax or entertain.  Spoil yourself in the spacious primary suite.  Offering a seating area, large custom walk in, lanai access and an oversized  en-suite with dual vanities, this is a true retreat!   Three guest rooms, with one on the front of the home perfect as office or den, make this floor plan ideal.   LET THE SUNSHINE IN with the three sets of siders leading to the showcase of this home, the private screened lanai! With  Southern exposure, a large covered area to dine and relax and surrounding  the heated POOL with double waterfall AND SPA, you can make this your own true Oasis!  This property  also has great curb appeal, a three car garage and is located on  a beautiful tree lined street just minutes from the main Clubhouse. River Strand just keeps getting better and better, with the pristine 27 holes of recently redesigned Arthur Hills golf running through the community, a clubhouse with RESTAURANT AND GRILLE ROOM, 2 community pools and spas, tiki bar, 6 satellite pools, 2 fitness centers and tennis and pickle ball courts too!   Choose from the  many social and fitness activities including live entertainment, racquet and golf leagues, numerous social clubs, fitness classes, pool parties and more!   IDEALLY LOCATED, minutes to I-75, which means quick access to dining, shopping and entertainment, and also close to the beautiful beaches of the Gulf Coast!  So come and start living your best Florida life, once you experience River Strand at it's best you may never want to leave!
